snippet.title: 710L1 48 inch Amber white lightbar
snippet.description:
Item No TBD-710L1Q 1200mm amber white led warning lightbar
Voltage 12V / 24V DC (choose one)
Product Description 0.25w led light
 "With controller 57-3K
First switch: front light power on/off
Second switch: front light power on/off
Third switch: front light power on/off"
 With 2 Mounting Brackets and hooks
Led Color Red,Blue,Amber,White,Green
Lens Color Red,Blue,Amber,transparent
Flash patterns About 4 types
Material  PC Lens & Aluminum Base
Operating Temperature -40 to 55(centigrade)
Cable 3.5 meter of cable provided
Product Size/N.W. 1210*340*234mm
Box Size/G.W. 1pc/1280*400*300mm/15.2kgs/ctn
